<section class="section" aria-labelledby="support-guide-title">
  <p class="eyebrow">Editable guidance</p>
  <h2 id="support-guide-title">Installation and plugin scanning</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Quit your host application before installing or updating a plug-in.</li>
    <li>Install only from the delivery location supplied with your product.</li>
    <li>Restart the host and run its plug-in scan or rescan command.</li>
    <li>On Apple silicon, use the native version of your host where available, then rescan.</li>
  </ol>
  <p>Common VST3 locations include <code>C:\Program Files\Common Files\VST3</code> on Windows and <code>/Library/Audio/Plug-Ins/VST3</code> or <code>~/Library/Audio/Plug-Ins/VST3</code> on macOS. Common AU locations include <code>/Library/Audio/Plug-Ins/Components</code> and <code>~/Library/Audio/Plug-Ins/Components</code>.</p>
</section>
